    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been so reliable and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a great ride that\u2019s ready to hit the road. It\u2019s super clean, runs like a dream, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. I'm sad to see it go, but I'm excited for it to start its next chapter with you! Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
