      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s still got plenty of zip? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it has been such a treat to own! It\u2019s in really nice shape, runs super smoothly, and has been well-loved over the years. It's perfect for someone who wants a solid, dependable vehicle that still looks sharp in the driveway. I've kept up with the maintenance, so it's ready to hit the road with you today. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
