      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example has been meticulously maintained with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive double VANOS overhaul, ensuring long-term structural and timing reliability. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox shifts with precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. The chassis is tightened with Bilstein B6 dampers and refreshed control arm bushings. While the finish exhibits minor road wear typical of a driven classic, the powertrain maintains excellent compression and a linear torque curve. A true enthusiast's spec, optimized for tactile feedback and visceral performance.",
